page.title: 05The Highworth Environment.
page.content: This piece of writing shows how many trees there are in the library car park and the churchyard. {The trees in {the car park.}There were 5 lime, 39 maple,14 ash and 1 fir tree.{The trees {in the churchyard.}There were 2 yew,23 lime,8 conifer,4 flowering trees,1 horse chestnut,16 shrubs,2 small trees 4 cherry and 3 almond leaved willows. We asked a number of people what there favourite wild flower or tree is this is the answers. 1 liked Mely Primrose 5 liked Cowslip 2 liked wild rose 1 liked daffidill 4 liked Daisy 5 liked Bluebell 4 liked Primrose 1 liked moondaisy 1 liked Poppy 4 liked Buttercup.These are some trees,6 liked oak 3 liked Willow 3 liked scymore 2 liked Beech 1 liked Acorn 1 liked Ash 1 liked Cherry 1 liked conifer 1 liked silver birch 1 liked Chestnut and 1 liked fir.
